    <section>
        <h2>Welcome to AN Courses!</h2>
        <p>Welcome to AN Courses, your premier destination for top-notch animation education! We are passionate about the art of animation and dedicated to helping aspiring animators turn their dreams into reality. Whether you're just starting out or looking to enhance your skills, our comprehensive courses are designed to cater to all levels of experience.</p>
