    <section>
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded in <%= new java.util.Date().getYear() + 1900 %>, AN Courses was born out of a love for animation and a desire to share that passion with the world. Our team of experienced animators and industry professionals came together with a vision to create a learning platform that is both accessible and inspiring. Over the years, we have grown into a vibrant community of students and educators, all united by a shared commitment to excellence in animation.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>At AN Courses, our mission is to provide high-quality animation education that empowers individuals to unleash their creativity and achieve their full potential. We believe that animation is not just a skill, but an art form that can tell powerful stories and evoke deep emotions. Our goal is to equip our students with the technical skills and artistic insight they need to succeed in the dynamic world of animation.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Comprehensive Courses:</strong> Our curriculum covers a wide range of topics, including 2D animation, 3D animation, character design, storyboarding, and more. Each course is meticulously crafted to ensure a balanced mix of theory and practical application.</li>
            <li><strong>Expert Instructors:</strong> Learn from the best in the industry. Our instructors are seasoned professionals with years of experience working on major animated films, TV shows, and video games. They bring real-world insights and hands-on knowledge to the classroom.</li>
            <li><strong>Flexible Learning:</strong> We understand that everyone has different schedules and learning preferences. That's why we offer flexible learning options, including online courses, live webinars, and in-person workshops, so you can learn at your own pace.</li>
            <li><strong>Community and Support:</strong> Join a community of like-minded individuals who share your passion for animation. Our forums and networking events provide opportunities to connect, collaborate, and grow together. Plus, our dedicated support team is always here to help you along your learning journey.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Proven Track Record:</strong> Thousands of students have successfully completed our courses and gone on to pursue successful careers in animation. Our alumni work in some of the most prestigious animation studios around the world.</li>
            <li><strong>Innovative Learning Tools:</strong> We utilize the latest technology and software in our courses, ensuring that you are learning with the tools used by professionals in the industry. Our interactive lessons and hands-on projects make learning engaging and effective.</li>
